## Phase 2c Refactor

Changes:
- No structural changes needed. feed.rs module is well-factored:
  - Public API: Tauri commands (select_past_note, request_note_deletion,
    confirm_note_deletion, cancel_note_deletion, fs_trash_file, feed_initial_state)
  - Internal helpers: fs_trash_file_impl (public for testing), make_*_snapshot
    constructors, parse_frontmatter_metadata (deterministic, testable)
  - DTOs: TrashErrorDto, FeedDomainSnapshotDto and sub-types (all with serde)
- +page.svelte layout is minimal and correct per REQ-FEED-023 and DESIGN.md.
- vitest.config.ts updated to include src/routes/__tests__/**/*.vitest.ts.

